data.description: This home is not just a property; it's a lifestyle. Well maintained, thoughtfully upgraded, and strategically positioned in an over-55 resort community, it offers a rare opportunity to experience the epitome of comfortable and stylish living. With its three bedrooms, flexible living spaces, recent renovations, and a location that guarantees stunning sunsets, this residence is indeed a must-see for those in search of a home that transcends expectations. Step inside to discover a meticulously designed interior where modern conveniences seamlessly merge with sophisticated aesthetics. LED lighting bathes the home in a warm and energy-efficient glow, while crown molding adds an extra layer of elegance to the living spaces. The heart of the home is the recently upgraded kitchen, where functionality meets style. Granite countertops and upgraded backsplash provide a luxurious backdrop for culinary endeavors. Recent appliances add a contemporary touch, ensuring a seamless cooking experience.
